08-08T05:52:05.000Z","msg":"請問點解721元朗事件只以非法集結拘捕，而728中西事件則以暴動罪控告？請問係點樣界定嫁？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（如果佢地推波俾律政司）要求第二日記得會請律政師到場釋疑。（林鄭話會搞跨界別記者會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"51efd2ae2fb603a6894444bcc9eb0a4635e0ff7a","tid":1431823,"uid":119485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:52:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/BmepMAH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBmepMAH.jpg&h=0ea49d1a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Yz5gCHn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYz5gCHn.png&h=a502547a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/pHFPXHp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpHFPXHp.jpg&h=3872d705&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66326aab5c4e882daf088458de6125d14e2eb802","tid":1431823,"uid":268094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:53:38.000Z","msg":"警方有否定性這兩個月示威活動是暴動？如果無，為何係和平理性表達訴求時，作出強力的攻擊？"},{"pid":"4333a5618c7a8d3960032c5c5ef34ee307c30247","tid":1431823,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:53:40.000Z","msg":"為何警隊係民居依然毫不忌諱地發射催淚煙，事前有冇考慮過該區地點既位置係根本不宜發出催淚煙？因為催淚彈係多次波及無辜民眾及逗留係屋企既市民！係屋企既市民冇出街都受到波及，警隊打算點樣處理？"},{"pid":"d010b23b1700415ab068cf1bfa5a50b98c6d1f08","tid":1431823,"uid":7818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:54:39.000Z","msg":"14K聲稱8.11吹雞血洗黑衣人<br />\n肛蛇會唔會去對依個情報作出部署<br />\n如果到時北角水馬陣圍封左係唔係唔洗出動<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5558c28d3488bb1b8867f78ebfacb4efec69533b","tid":1431823,"uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:55:26.000Z","msg":"1. 有無用過期催淚彈，Yes or No<br />\nIf Yes，點解要用，用咗幾多粒，邊區用，有無嚴重後遺症<br />\nIf No，點解有大量催淚彈圖片寫住EXP2016年<br />\nIf 唔肯答，幾時先肯答，市民有好強烈知情權<br />\n<br />\n2. 7.21 元朗恐襲幾時落案告所拘捕人仕<br />\nIf 唔肯答，幾時先肯答，市民有好強烈知情權<br />\n<br />\n3. 7.27 元朗示威點解會射催淚彈上西鐵路軌，危害乘客同職員安全<br />\nIf 唔肯答，幾時先肯答，市民有好強烈知情權<br />\n<br />\n4. 8.5點解有催淚彈由金鐘高空射落路面，發射位置係邊，點解要咁做<br />\nIf 唔肯答，幾時先肯答，市民有好強烈知情權"},{"pid":"35b64fcee50f7bd3adde11d1e3cf67de7d38ea62","tid":1431823,"uid":86741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:56:47.000Z","msg":"唔該用返 警犬記者會 做標題 唔好幫記者會d 阿sir 出名，降低佢地關注度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac7508b5d7b2d0ffb284f1290a0a1c5b77e16a92","tid":1431823,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:57:06.000Z","msg":"7月14日的沙田示威事件中，警方係沙田新城市廣場附既多條道路、商場通道、出入口設立封鎖線，在場多名立法會議員要求警方指出示威者可撤離路線，但警方未有回答。<br />\n<br />\n請問當日係想驅散示威者定圍堵示威者？<br />\n<br />\n如果想驅散點解唔指出示威者可以撤離既路線？"},{"pid":"76c40d25c70717cd5b08cdf73f02ead51e82c148","tid":1431823,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:57:46.000Z","msg":"黑社會都有記者會?"},{"pid":"ed80a44fd9ba3cedb750101a5d333ce6b801c8f3","tid":1431823,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35b64fcee50f7bd3adde11d1e3cf67de7d38ea62","tid":1431823,"uid":86741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:56:47.000Z","msg":"唔該用返 警犬記者會 做標題 唔好幫記者會d 阿sir 出名，降低佢地關注度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:57:46.000Z","msg":"聽日開既時候改返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝提醒"},{"pid":"d5c93a3768374cf9ea16961edcf848ec885f44d0","tid":1431823,"uid":265339,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:01:23.000Z","msg":"雖然話強烈建議用問題推post，但真係推到好慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唯有用返推黎推post"},{"pid":"